s the unmistakable work of a brilliantly individualistic poet, brought to modern English readers by Raffel's poetic translation in a metric form invented specifically to reflect Chrétien's narrative speed and tone.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Mai 2023) 7aPOETRY / European / General.2bisacsh1 aDuggan, Joseph J., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aTroyes, Chrétien de, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertYale University Press eBook-Package Archive Pre-2000z97831105380140 cprintz978030007020040uhttps://doi.org/10.12987/978030014413040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780300144130423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780300144130/original  a978-3-11-053801-4  Yale University Press eBook-Package Archive Pre-2000b2000  aEBA_FAO  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-UCY